<P>
   SIBLEY-OBIT _ Long-time Atlanta Journal-Constitution columnist
and Southern author Celestine Sibley died of cancer Sunday morning.
She was 85. (Emerson, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 10-15. WITH
PHOTOS.
</P>
<P>
   EDs: Moving in the (a) General News and (l) Lifestyle
categories.
</P>
