<P>
   FBN-JETS-PACKERS (Hempstead, N.Y.) _ Folo on the Jets-Packers
game. By Gerald Eskenazi.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-GIANTS (Albany, N.Y.) _ A feature on the Giants. By Thomas
George.
</P>
