<TEXT>
<P>
   The Seattle Post-Intelligencer plans to move the additional
story for clients of the NYTimes News Service for editions of
Monday, Aug. 16, and thereafter. If you have any questions, please
call Veronica Villarreal at (206) 448-8342.
</P>
<P>
   FOOD-OWEN-COLUMN (Undated) _ I lust for salt. Anchovies, chipped
beef, green olives, smoked salmon, salted peanuts, dill pickles and
prosciutto ham all occupy prominent places on my shopping lists.
</P>
<P>
   By John Owen. (Story will move in the ``d'' category.)
</P>
</TEXT>
